description: Theta series of hypothetical extremal 3-modular even 36-dimensional lattice with minimal norm 8 and det = 3^18.
references: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 204.
links: H.-G. Quebbemann, Modular lattices in Euclidean spaces, J. Number Theory, 54 (1995), 190-202.
E. M. Rains and N. J. A. Sloane, The Shadow Theory of Modular and Unimodular Lattices, J. Number Theory, 73 (1998), 359-389.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Eric Rains
